{
  "text": "Moreover, the new smart industry must have the capability of reacting to new changes in the market or to different requirements from the customers. This is where the concept of agile manufacturing [CITATION_1] is used in order to generate new adaptations to the manufacturing process, keeping high quality in the products in shorter times or producing just in time.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "69787957"
  },
  "bib_entries": {
    "69787957": {
      "title": "Agility capability maturity framework",
      "abstract": "Abstract Agility is the strategy that allows contemporary companies cope with dynamics and turbulence of contemporary market. As it is complex approach it requires maturity to fully benefit from expected results. The paper strives to present Agility Capability Maturity as a model that can be used to diagnose level of agility that organization represents and suggest further steps to be taken to improve agility and in the same agility capability maturity level. Theoretical background is briefly discussed and basic assumptions of the methodology are presented."
    }
  }
}